text: Acha or ACHA may refer to: *Acha, Coll, Scottish village *Acha (doll), a character in Namco's 1986 arcade game, Toy Pop *Acha (name), list of people with the name *Acha Mountain Fortress, an earthen fortress *General Acha, town in La Pampa Province, Argentina *American College Health Association *American Collegiate Hockey Association *A name for Digitaria exilis, a species of fonio ==See also== *Acha Dhin, 2015 Malayalam film
